  "description": "A still life photograph features a whole lime positioned above a halved lime. The lime is a vibrant green color, with some textural imperfections on its rind. The halved lime reveals its juicy, segmented interior, displaying a radial pattern of pale yellow pulp and juice-filled vesicles. The backdrop is a dark, textured surface, which enhances the contrast with the bright green of the citrus fruit. The lighting is soft, accentuating the freshness and natural quality of the limes.",
